The Best .vimrc Ever (tm)
===

Requirements:
---

     * Ruby 1.8.7
     * Vim


Installation:
---

    sudo yum -y install gcc make ruby ruby-devel vim
    mkdir ~/.vim
    git clone git://github.com/dmalan/vimrc.git ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc .vimrc
    cd ~/.vim/ruby/command-t
    ruby extconf.rb
    make
